  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the squid and cook for 2-3 minutes, until lightly browned.",
    "Add the white wine and cook until the liquid has almost completely evaporated.",
    "Add the fish stock, tomato paste, and lemon juice. Stir to combine.",
